  <brief_title>Sofosbuvir/Velpatasvir/Voxilaprevir Fixed-Dose Combination for 12 Weeks in Adults Who Participated in a Prior Gilead-Sponsored HCV Treatment Study</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open-Label Study to Evaluate the Safety And Efficacy of Sofosbuvir/Velpatasvir/Voxilaprevir Fixed-Dose Combination for 12 Weeks in Subjects Who Participated in a Prior Gilead-Sponsored HCV Treatment Study</official_title>
