  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary objectives of this study are to determine the efficacy of treatment with
      sofosbuvir/velpatasvir/voxilaprevir (SOF/VEL/VOX) fixed-dose combination (FDC) for 12 weeks
      as measured by the proportion of participants with sustained viral response 12 weeks after
      cessation of treatment (SVR12) and to evaluate the safety and tolerability of treatment with
      SOF/VEL/VOX FDC.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
